import styleContainer from './TaskList.module.css'

const TaskCircleProgress = () => {
    <svg
    width="24"
    height="24"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    className={styleContainer.circularProgressbar}
  >
    <circle
      className={styleContainer.circleBackground}
      cx="12"
      cy="12"
      r="11"
      strokeWidth="2px"
    ></circle>
    <circle
      class={styleContainer.circleProgress}
      cx="12"
      cy="12"
      r="11"
      strokeWidth="2px"
      transform="rotate(-90 12 12)"
      style={{strokeDasharray: 69.115, strokeDashoffset: 69.115}}
    ></circle>
  </svg>
}

export default TaskCircleProgress;
